1
00:00:00,000 --> 00:00:05,000
A bouncing blue light led a
tiny fox beyond the garden gate.

2
00:00:05,000 --> 00:00:10,000
In the willow pond, the fox learned that a
tiny bird had lost the nest it called home.

3
00:00:10,000 --> 00:00:15,000
What began as a rescue mission grew harder
when the golden button slipped out of reach.

4
00:00:15,000 --> 00:00:20,000
The thoughtful fox decided to reach the stranded friend
and turned fallen petals into tiny guiding flags.

5
00:00:20,000 --> 00:00:25,000
The plan worked, bringing a safe
rescue for everyone in the willow pond.

6
00:00:25,000 --> 00:00:30,000
Everyone laughed as the helpful object gave one joyful bounce.
The golden button softly echoed the adventure's beginning.
